cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition and natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it involves processing audio signals. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses neural networks to learn and make predictions. Finally, it could be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it involves designing a system for speech recognition.
